                   catalyze a biogeochemical process. Thermodynamics and
                   kinetics of electron transfer reactions with both the
                   electron donor (e.g., hydrogen sulfide as a bulk
                   reductant) and the terminal electron acceptor (e.g.,
                   nitroaromatic explosives in contaminant degradation),
                   and stability towards irreversible side reactions are
